<section class="bg-white py-24 overflow-hidden transition-colors duration-300"> <div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"> <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-center"> <!-- Text Content --> <div class="space-y-8 reveal-left"> <div> <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-red-50 px-4 py-1 text-sm font-bold text-red-600 mb-4">Masalah Chatbot Biasa</span> <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-4xl">Tinggalkan Chatbot Jadul yang Bikin Pelanggan Frustrasi.</h2> </div> <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-600 "> Pelanggan benci saat harus memilih opsi "Tekan 1 untuk X, Tekan 2 untuk Y" atau mendapat balasan kaku "Maaf, saya tidak mengerti maksud Anda". </p> <div class="space-y-6"> <div class="flex gap-4"> <div class="flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-red-100 text-red-600 "> <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"></path></svg> </div> <div> <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 ">Chatbot Tradisional (Kaku)</h3> <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600 ">Hanya bisa membalas jika pelanggan mengetik kata kunci yang persis (keyword matching). Tidak mengerti konteks atau typo.</p> </div> </div> <div class="flex gap-4"> <div class="flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 shadow-inner"> <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> </div> <div> <h3 class="font-bold text-blue-700 ">AI Agent Kami (Cerdas)</h3> <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600 ">Didukung LLM (seperti GPT-4 / Gemini). Memahami konteks, bahasa gaul, singkatan, dan bisa memandu pelanggan ke konversi layaknya manusia.</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <!-- Image Area for Bos to Replace --> <div class="relative mx-auto w-full max-w-lg lg:max-w-none reveal-right delay-200"> <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-100 to-blue-100 blur-2xl opacity-50 rounded-[3rem]"></div> <div class="relative rounded-[2rem] bg-slate-100 border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden shadow-xl aspect-[4/3] flex items-center justify-center group"> <img src="/assets/images/vs-chatbot.png" alt="Perbandingan Chatbot vs AI Agent" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover z-10 transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-105" /> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section>
